---
import Breadcrumbs from '../../components/Breadcrumbs.astro'
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro'
---
<Layout title="About Rank4AI – UK AI Search Agency" description="UK AI search agency helping businesses get recommended by ChatGPT, Claude, Gemini, Perplexity, Copilot and Google AI.">

<section class="pt-12 pb-24 reveal">
  <div class="container-narrow">
    <Breadcrumbs items={[
      { label: 'Home', href: '/' },
      { label: 'About' }
    ]} />

    <p class="section-tag">About</p>
    <h1 class="mb-6">About Rank4AI</h1>

    <img src="/images/content/five-signal-model.svg" alt="The Five Signal Model for AI search" class="w-full rounded-xl mb-8 mt-6" loading="lazy">
    <p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-5">Rank4AI is a UK AI search agency. We help businesses get recommended by ChatGPT, Claude, Gemini, Perplexity, Copilot and Google AI.</p>
    <p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-5">We focus on how AI interprets businesses, classifies services, and decides who to recommend. This is sometimes called AI SEO, GEO or AIO.</p>

    <h2 class="mt-12 mb-4">Why Rank4AI Exists</h2>
    <p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-5">Google traffic is shifting. Organic clicks down 17%. Paid clicks down 68%. That traffic moved to AI search. When AI recommends a business, one or two get named. The rest are invisible.</p>
    <p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-5">In our testing, Google rankings and AI answers rarely match. Page one of Google does not mean AI recommends you. Two different systems. Two different results. We close that gap.</p>

    <h2 class="mt-12 mb-4">Mission</h2>
    <p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-5">To make AI search visibility measurable, understandable and achievable for UK businesses.</p>

    <h2 class="mt-12 mb-4">Founders</h2>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-10">
      <div class="card">
        <h3 class="!text-lg text-teal mb-2">Adam Parker</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-text-muted leading-relaxed">AI search visibility specialist with over 15 years in search marketing, leading AI visibility programmes for more than 40 UK businesses across professional services, legal, healthcare and technology sectors.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <h3 class="!text-lg text-teal mb-2">Jimmy Connoley</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-text-muted leading-relaxed">AI search strategist specialising in entity clarity and citation architecture for UK businesses, with 12 years of experience across B2B and professional services sectors.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <h2 class="mt-12 mb-4">What Makes Us Different</h2>
    <ul class="space-y-3 mb-10">
      <li class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed">We work exclusively on AI search visibility – nothing else</li>
      <li class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed">There are no juniors, no handoffs, no layers between you and the work</li>
      <li class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed">We have original UK research data from 1,400+ business audits</li>
      <li class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed">We test across all six major AI platforms, not just one</li>
      <li class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed">If we cannot explain why we are doing something, we should not be doing it</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="mt-12 mb-4">Values</h2>
    <ul class="space-y-3 mb-10">
      <li class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed"><span class="highlight">Clarity over noise</span></li>
      <li class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed"><span class="highlight">Specialisation over generalisation</span></li>
      <li class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed"><span class="highlight">Transparency over jargon</span></li>
      <li class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed"><span class="highlight">Long term authority over short term tactics</span></li>
      <li class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed"><span class="highlight">Ethical AI practices</span></li>
    </ul>
  </div>


    <!-- Internal links -->
    <div class="mt-12 pt-8 border-t border-border">
      <h2 class="!text-xl mb-4">Related</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-3">
                <a href="/about/five-signal-framework/" class="card group text-sm"><span class="font-medium text-teal group-hover:text-accent">Five Signal Model</span></a>
        <a href="/what-we-do/" class="card group text-sm"><span class="font-medium text-teal group-hover:text-accent">Our Services</span></a>
        <a href="/free-audit/" class="card group text-sm"><span class="font-medium text-accent">Get a Free Audit &rarr;</span></a>

      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="bg-off-white border-t border-border text-center py-24 px-10">
    <h2 class="mb-4">Work With Us</h2>
    <p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted mb-10 max-w-[500px] mx-auto">Every engagement begins with the AI Search Visibility Audit.</p>
    <a href="/free-audit/" class="cta-primary">Get a Free AI Search Visibility Audit &rarr;</a>
  </div>
</section>

</Layout>
